Changes to LLC Laptop Loan Policy effective December 18, 2023. (No specific information extracted related to the college program.)

3D printing services are now available at St. James and Casa LLCCs.
Costs $3 per hour and is available between Monday–Friday, 10am–4pm.
Print jobs exceeding 4 hours may not be approved and wait times vary depending on the length of the queue.
Designs can be made or downloaded from websites such as Thingiverse or YouMagin.
Use of 3D printer is limited to lawful purposes only, and printing weapons, unsafe or offensive objects, sexually-explicit materials, and intellectual property rights infringement is prohibited.
Only library staff have hands-on access to the 3D printers.
